00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:11,420
In physics and signal processing, the peaks concentrate the signal's energetic and temporal structure.

122
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:18,660
The space between the peaks is largely predictable if you know the dynamics of the system generating it.

123
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:21,140
Think of human vocal cords vibrating.

