520
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:13,800
Infrasound is a field-like effect.

521
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:15,500
It fills the whole room.

522
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:21,020
So, in hyperbionic text, the haptic extension translates into global layout modulation.

523
00:37:21,020 --> 00:37:26,900
If the speaker's voice has heavy sub-bass, the bass line of the entire page might drift slightly,

